<topic class="Popup" template="Default" modified="2024-02-05T18:46:47.203Z" lasteditedby="44785" version="2" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="../../../helpproject.xsd">
  <title>Spin-Box-Tool</title>
  <keywords>
    <keyword>Spin-box tool</keyword>
  </keywords>
  <body>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><table styleclass="PopupTable" rowcount="2" colcount="2">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:140px; background-color:#ffffff;">
          <para styleclass="Normal"><image src="MD--Pop-Dialog-Dimension-Spinbox-popup.png" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"><title>Spin-Box tool</title><caption><![CDATA[Spin-Box tool [the arrowheads in the 'green-box'].]]></caption></image></para>
        </td>
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal;">The </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small">Spin-Box tool</text><image src="Red-14-3.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image><image src="Red-14-4.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image><text style="font-weight:bold; font-style:italic;">&#32;</text>is a convenient way to edit the data-value of a parameter in a dialog.</para>
          <list id="0" type="ul" listtype="bullet" formatstring="&#183;" format-charset="SYMBOL_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Popup Box" style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:10pt; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="VariableName-small">To edit the parameter value</text><image src="Red-14-1b.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image><text styleclass="Image Caption">&#32;</text><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal;">by the </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small">Spin-Increment</text><image src="Red-14-2.gif" scale="100.00%" figurelistinclude="0"></image>, click<text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal;"> the </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small">top</text><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal;"> arrow buttons</text><image src="Red-14-3.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal;">&#32;</text></li>
          </list>
          <list id="1" type="ul" listtype="bullet" formatstring="&#183;" format-charset="SYMBOL_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Popup Box" style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:10pt; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="VariableName-small">Edit the Spin-Increment</text><image src="Red-14-2.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:italic;">: </text><br/><text style="font-weight:normal;">Click</text><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal;"> the </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small">bottom</text><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal;"> arrow buttons</text><image src="Red-14-4.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal;"> to edit the </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small">Spin-Increment</text> by factors of 10.</li>
          </list>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td colspan="2">
          <list id="2" type="ul" listtype="bullet" formatstring="&#183;" format-charset="SYMBOL_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="VariableName-small" style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:10pt; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="VariableName-small">Show or hide the Spin-Box tool<image src="Red-14-3.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Popup Box" figurelistinclude="0"></image><image src="Red-14-4.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Popup Box" figurelistinclude="0"></image><text styleclass="Popup Box">, double-click in the data-box</text><image src="Red-14-1b.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image><text styleclass="Popup Box"> to toggle between </text>Show or Hide the spin-box tool<text styleclass="Popup Box">.</text></li>
          </list>
          <list id="3" type="ul" listtype="bullet" formatstring="&#183;" format-charset="SYMBOL_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Popup Box" style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:10pt; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="Popup Box">To use the <text styleclass="VariableName-small">Zero/Round/Copy/Paste shortcut menu</text>, right-click in the data-box<image src="Red-14-1b.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image><text styleclass="Image Caption">.</text></li>
          </list>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
  </body>
